[ROOSTER CROWS]

00:37:24.025 --> 00:37:24.825 align:middle line:90%


00:37:24.825 --> 00:37:54.560 align:middle line:90%
[NON-ENGLISH SINGING]

00:37:54.560 --> 00:37:55.750 align:middle line:90%
>> [INAUDIBLE] cinema.

00:37:55.750 --> 00:37:58.170 align:middle line:90%
[INAUDIBLE] speakers.

00:37:58.170 --> 00:37:59.050 align:middle line:90%
Ready?

