Three.

00:38:04.776 --> 00:38:12.712 align:middle line:84%
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

00:38:12.712 --> 00:38:23.876 align:middle line:90%


00:38:23.876 --> 00:38:27.780 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:38:27.780 --> 00:38:30.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Through the programs of
Village Action, Auroville,

00:38:30.690 --> 00:38:33.810 align:middle line:84%
