would like to give to the
surrounding 30,000 villagers

00:38:37.500 --> 00:38:40.950 align:middle line:84%
the means for their
socioeconomic independence,

00:38:40.950 --> 00:38:44.210 align:middle line:84%
paying particular attention
to women and youth.

00:38:44.210 --> 00:38:46.230 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:38:46.230 --> 00:38:49.470 align:middle line:84%
>> In the beginning, I was
acutely aware of my limits.

00:38:49.470 --> 00:38:51.990 align:middle line:84%
Now I know that women
can be active and do more

00:38:51.990 --> 00:38:53.010 align:middle line:90%
for the village.

00:38:53.010 --> 00:38:55.020 align:middle line:84%
This confidence I gained
through Village Action.

00:38:55.020 --> 00:38:57.684 align:middle line:90%


00:38:57.684 --> 00:39:02.190 align:middle line:84%
>> Auroville's economy needs
the support of Tamil workers,

