just as these, in return,
need the work that is offered

00:39:05.310 --> 00:39:09.480 align:middle line:84%
in a variety of sectors,
administration, handicrafts,

00:39:09.480 --> 00:39:11.420 align:middle line:90%
industry.

00:39:11.420 --> 00:39:13.530 align:middle line:84%
Mother's vision was
a city where there

00:39:13.530 --> 00:39:16.530 align:middle line:84%
would be no exchange
of money, but the dream

00:39:16.530 --> 00:39:18.440 align:middle line:90%
has yet to be realized.

00:39:18.440 --> 00:39:21.120 align:middle line:84%
And a truly alternative
economic system

00:39:21.120 --> 00:39:23.770 align:middle line:90%
is still barely off the ground.

00:39:23.770 --> 00:39:27.750 align:middle line:84%
However, education, health
care, and culture are free.

00:39:27.750 --> 00:39:30.490 align:middle line:84%
And the central fund
provides an income,

00:39:30.490 --> 00:39:32.400 align:middle line:84%
which is not
considered a salary,

00:39:32.400 --> 00:39:34.950 align:middle line:84%
for those working for the
development of the city.

00:39:34.950 --> 00:39:38.810 align:middle line:90%


00:39:38.810 --> 00:39:40.570 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:39:40.570 --> 00:39:42.972 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, the rules of
the marketplace exist.

00:39:42.972 --> 00:39:45.180 align:middle line:84%
At the end of the month, I
have to provide for myself

00:39:45.180 --> 00:39:48.060 align:middle line:84%
as well as cover the
salaries of the employees.

00:39:48.060 --> 00:39:51.090 align:middle line:10%
There should also be
profit, but I work in order

00:39:51.090 --> 00:39:52.840 align:middle line:10%
to give money to Auroville.

00:39:52.840 --> 00:39:55.360 align:middle line:84%
My goal is to be able to
stay here and contribute

00:39:55.360 --> 00:39:56.930 align:middle line:90%
to Auroville growth.

00:39:56.930 --> 00:39:58.680 align:middle line:84%
That is what everybody
else has done here.

00:39:58.680 --> 00:40:01.440 align:middle line:90%


00:40:01.440 --> 00:40:03.720 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:40:03.720 --> 00:40:07.470 align:middle line:10%
>> All sorts of services are
provided for free in Auroville,

00:40:07.470 --> 00:40:12.870 align:middle line:10%
Tai Chi courses, massage,
theater and cinema are free.

00:40:12.870 --> 00:40:16.590 align:middle line:84%
If someone needs clothing,
a second-hand store,

00:40:16.590 --> 00:40:19.080 align:middle line:90%
the free store exists.

00:40:19.080 --> 00:40:21.120 align:middle line:10%
If someone does not
have the means for food,

00:40:21.120 --> 00:40:23.490 align:middle line:10%
it is free, as are
many other services.

00:40:23.490 --> 00:40:29.440 align:middle line:90%


00:40:29.440 --> 00:40:33.990 align:middle line:10%
>> This store is a
means of free exchange.

00:40:33.990 --> 00:40:36.720 align:middle line:10%
People bring things,
and they take

00:40:36.720 --> 00:40:39.400 align:middle line:10%
what they need to be taking.

00:40:39.400 --> 00:40:42.030 align:middle line:90%
>> So they don't have to pay?

00:40:42.030 --> 00:40:43.930 align:middle line:90%
>> It's totally without money.

00:40:43.930 --> 00:40:46.390 align:middle line:84%
It's like people have
to be free, happy.

00:40:46.390 --> 00:40:49.315 align:middle line:84%
I know, this is the only place
in Auroville, free exchange.

00:40:49.315 --> 00:40:59.820 align:middle line:90%


00:40:59.820 --> 00:41:03.380 align:middle line:84%
>> If a Tamil people went to
Europe, you know, uneducated.

00:41:03.380 --> 00:41:05.180 align:middle line:84%
I know a lot of
people like that.

00:41:05.180 --> 00:41:07.910 align:middle line:10%
In two years, they speak the
language wherever they went,

00:41:07.910 --> 00:41:10.340 align:middle line:10%
whether it is in France
or Italy or Switzerland,

00:41:10.340 --> 00:41:11.697 align:middle line:10%
they become part of that.

00:41:11.697 --> 00:41:13.655 align:middle line:84%
You know, particularly,
the first thing they do

00:41:13.655 --> 00:41:15.410 align:middle line:90%
is learning the language.

00:41:15.410 --> 00:41:18.800 align:middle line:84%
Only through that you learn
more into that culture.

00:41:18.800 --> 00:41:21.705 align:middle line:84%
And here you can't
say one people

00:41:21.705 --> 00:41:24.080 align:middle line:84%
have learned this
local language.

00:41:24.080 --> 00:41:27.020 align:middle line:84%
Maybe they try the
needed part, you know?

00:41:27.020 --> 00:41:29.840 align:middle line:10%
Needed part means
what they can handle.

00:41:29.840 --> 00:41:32.250 align:middle line:10%
But not the deeper
side, what the cultures

00:41:32.250 --> 00:41:35.810 align:middle line:10%
be, what nobody have
learned in the cities.

00:41:35.810 --> 00:41:42.810 align:middle line:90%


00:41:42.810 --> 00:41:44.580 align:middle line:84%
>> I like my culture
so much, you know?

00:41:44.580 --> 00:41:46.710 align:middle line:84%
Seeing this
spirituality is there.

00:41:46.710 --> 00:41:50.250 align:middle line:10%
If you go to the temple, you see
that all the people are really

00:41:50.250 --> 00:41:53.007 align:middle line:10%
praying, and it's even--
it's a one minute.

00:41:53.007 --> 00:41:55.590 align:middle line:84%
They're praying maybe-- I don't
know how much they concentrate

00:41:55.590 --> 00:41:56.790 align:middle line:90%
on what they--

00:41:56.790 --> 00:41:58.710 align:middle line:84%
but see that the
vibration is good

00:41:58.710 --> 00:42:00.370 align:middle line:84%
and see you get
a good atmosphere

00:42:00.370 --> 00:42:03.170 align:middle line:84%
and so you feel inside
that God is there,

00:42:03.170 --> 00:42:07.140 align:middle line:84%
then that will make
you feel yourself, om.

00:42:07.140 --> 00:42:08.198 align:middle line:90%
That's very simple.

00:42:08.198 --> 00:42:10.490 align:middle line:84%
You don't need to go through
all this yogi or whatever.

00:42:10.490 --> 00:42:19.770 align:middle line:90%


00:42:19.770 --> 00:42:23.250 align:middle line:10%
>> We must determine that
unsustainable consumption,

00:42:23.250 --> 00:42:27.780 align:middle line:10%
unsustainable lifestyles, as
well as unacceptable poverty,

00:42:27.780 --> 00:42:29.920 align:middle line:10%
both should become
problems of the past.

00:42:29.920 --> 00:42:30.720 align:middle line:10%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:42:30.720 --> 00:42:34.470 align:middle line:10%
>> The essential thing is to ask
oneself what is one's searching

00:42:34.470 --> 00:42:35.320 align:middle line:10%
for.

00:42:35.320 --> 00:42:37.500 align:middle line:10%
What is it that one wants?

00:42:37.500 --> 00:42:40.170 align:middle line:84%
Our Western society today
is one that does not

00:42:40.170 --> 00:42:42.120 align:middle line:90%
think in terms of the future.

00:42:42.120 --> 00:42:44.400 align:middle line:10%
And because of
that, it is guilty,

00:42:44.400 --> 00:42:46.560 align:middle line:10%
and it will therefore be
necessary to establish

00:42:46.560 --> 00:42:51.270 align:middle line:10%
another type of society,
another way of living together.

00:42:51.270 --> 00:42:54.420 align:middle line:84%
The big advantage of today's
technological progress

00:42:54.420 --> 00:42:56.640 align:middle line:84%
that has put us in
touch with each other

00:42:56.640 --> 00:42:59.790 align:middle line:84%
is that we will be obliged
to create a society that

00:42:59.790 --> 00:43:01.470 align:middle line:90%
will include everyone.

00:43:01.470 --> 00:43:05.070 align:middle line:84%
And not only me, the
Westerner, the Frenchman.

00:43:05.070 --> 00:43:06.840 align:middle line:90%
That's just not possible.

00:43:06.840 --> 00:43:09.780 align:middle line:84%
I must come up with something
that is for all humanity.

00:43:09.780 --> 00:43:48.030 align:middle line:90%


00:43:48.030 --> 00:43:50.910 align:middle line:90%
>> In fact, [NON-ENGLISH].

00:43:50.910 --> 00:43:54.180 align:middle line:10%
>> Building individual houses
with great distances in between

00:43:54.180 --> 00:43:59.560 align:middle line:10%
them as one does today is simply
not a sustainable development.

00:43:59.560 --> 00:44:02.220 align:middle line:10%
It can, of course, satisfy
our childhood dream

00:44:02.220 --> 00:44:05.460 align:middle line:10%
of having a house,
garden, and space,

00:44:05.460 --> 00:44:08.490 align:middle line:10%
but it creates infrastructure,
transport, communication

00:44:08.490 --> 00:44:13.470 align:middle line:10%
problems, as well as problems
of environmental urbanism.

00:44:13.470 --> 00:44:16.830 align:middle line:84%
All that creates a
different type of sociology.

00:44:16.830 --> 00:44:20.550 align:middle line:84%
The challenge of a city like
ours is also one of density.

00:44:20.550 --> 00:44:22.590 align:middle line:84%
How to solve the
problem of density

00:44:22.590 --> 00:44:25.260 align:middle line:90%
without alienating individuals.

00:44:25.260 --> 00:44:27.750 align:middle line:84%
This is one amongst
many great challenges.

00:44:27.750 --> 00:44:34.230 align:middle line:90%


00:44:34.230 --> 00:44:37.860 align:middle line:84%
>> So this we would put
in the internet where?

00:44:37.860 --> 00:44:40.450 align:middle line:84%
>> The internet, and then also
it's coming out in booklet.

00:44:40.450 --> 00:44:42.572 align:middle line:84%
>> But in which section
of the internet?

00:44:42.572 --> 00:44:43.760 align:middle line:90%
How do you want to use it?

00:44:43.760 --> 00:44:45.210 align:middle line:90%
Do you know?

00:44:45.210 --> 00:44:47.350 align:middle line:90%
>> It's more educational.

00:44:47.350 --> 00:44:49.360 align:middle line:84%
>> So we put it in
the Open Section?

00:44:49.360 --> 00:44:52.360 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, that could be
one of the possible areas,

00:44:52.360 --> 00:44:53.971 align:middle line:90%
but it is yet to be finalized.

00:44:53.971 --> 00:44:57.900 align:middle line:90%


00:44:57.900 --> 00:45:01.980 align:middle line:84%
>> We are aware that the
world is looking at us.

00:45:01.980 --> 00:45:07.230 align:middle line:84%
And we try to be clear
about our trial and errors.

00:45:07.230 --> 00:45:09.600 align:middle line:84%
We have some lenders
to go through.

00:45:09.600 --> 00:45:12.120 align:middle line:84%
We are all just
humans who come here.

00:45:12.120 --> 00:45:15.300 align:middle line:10%
So this is the main
challenge, to show

00:45:15.300 --> 00:45:18.060 align:middle line:10%
Auroville in its entirety.

00:45:18.060 --> 00:45:20.130 align:middle line:10%
And this is also the main
challenge of our life

00:45:20.130 --> 00:45:23.467 align:middle line:10%
here, to live this
in its entirety.

00:45:23.467 --> 00:45:26.450 align:middle line:90%


00:45:26.450 --> 00:45:30.560 align:middle line:84%
>> Everybody takes
Mother's dream their way,

00:45:30.560 --> 00:45:33.360 align:middle line:90%
like they understand her dream.

00:45:33.360 --> 00:45:35.570 align:middle line:90%
It's a controversy sometimes.

00:45:35.570 --> 00:45:41.240 align:middle line:10%
And I feel very
often, very often, I

00:45:41.240 --> 00:45:45.020 align:middle line:10%
stand up in the morning, and
I say, I can't do it anymore.

00:45:45.020 --> 00:45:45.980 align:middle line:90%
I can't do it.

00:45:45.980 --> 00:45:48.950 align:middle line:84%
And you know, if I
didn't have that belief

00:45:48.950 --> 00:45:51.470 align:middle line:84%
that it's possible
to do it and to have

00:45:51.470 --> 00:45:53.930 align:middle line:84%
the strength of the
community that they're all

00:45:53.930 --> 00:45:57.580 align:middle line:84%
going the same road, and they're
all following the same road,

00:45:57.580 --> 00:45:58.920 align:middle line:90%
I think I never could do it.

00:45:58.920 --> 00:45:59.720 align:middle line:90%
You know?

00:45:59.720 --> 00:46:01.880 align:middle line:90%
And it's every morning, really.

00:46:01.880 --> 00:46:06.050 align:middle line:84%
It's every morning, a
struggle to go through it.

00:46:06.050 --> 00:46:08.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Based on a system that
could be described as a total

00:46:08.930 --> 00:46:12.950 align:middle line:84%
democracy, Auroville is once
again confronted by the simple

00:46:12.950 --> 00:46:15.980 align:middle line:84%
condition of the human
beings who live there.

00:46:15.980 --> 00:46:19.800 align:middle line:84%
It is not easy to know how to
use power, not easy to know

00:46:19.800 --> 00:46:23.030 align:middle line:84%
the practical daily ways that
respect the visionary concepts

00:46:23.030 --> 00:46:24.470 align:middle line:90%
of the beginning.

00:46:24.470 --> 00:46:27.830 align:middle line:84%
It is not always easy to meet
the expectations or confidence

00:46:27.830 --> 00:46:30.290 align:middle line:84%
shown by the Indian
government, that

00:46:30.290 --> 00:46:34.550 align:middle line:84%
nonetheless keeps a close watch
for any serious deviations.

00:46:34.550 --> 00:46:37.380 align:middle line:10%
Despite all this, perhaps
because of all this,

00:46:37.380 --> 00:46:40.200 align:middle line:10%
Auroville continues to grow.

00:46:40.200 --> 00:46:45.110 align:middle line:84%
>> I, myself, I'm really
dreaming of many young people

00:46:45.110 --> 00:46:46.970 align:middle line:90%
with skills coming in.

00:46:46.970 --> 00:46:51.170 align:middle line:10%
And it's a little bit my
wish in this two years

00:46:51.170 --> 00:46:57.500 align:middle line:10%
to come to be helpful in
facilitating kind of place

00:46:57.500 --> 00:46:59.610 align:middle line:10%
where young people with
little money could come.

00:46:59.610 --> 00:47:03.350 align:middle line:10%
Then it is difficult
now for young people.

00:47:03.350 --> 00:47:05.750 align:middle line:84%
Because you have to bring
not only the money for one

00:47:05.750 --> 00:47:08.690 align:middle line:84%
year, but also you
have to bring the money

00:47:08.690 --> 00:47:10.130 align:middle line:90%
to establish yourself.

00:47:10.130 --> 00:47:12.350 align:middle line:84%
And that saddens me
right now, because I

00:47:12.350 --> 00:47:16.513 align:middle line:84%
feel the power is
in that generation.

00:47:16.513 --> 00:47:24.090 align:middle line:90%


00:47:24.090 --> 00:47:29.970 align:middle line:10%
>> To speak about the future of
Auroville in my understanding,

00:47:29.970 --> 00:47:34.150 align:middle line:10%
it means putting a certain
concept on the future

00:47:34.150 --> 00:47:35.430 align:middle line:10%
of Auroville.

00:47:35.430 --> 00:47:40.030 align:middle line:84%
It means putting your ideas
on the future of Auroville.

00:47:40.030 --> 00:47:46.110 align:middle line:84%
And I think this is precisely
what we should not do more

00:47:46.110 --> 00:47:49.730 align:middle line:90%
than our founders have done.

00:47:49.730 --> 00:47:56.580 align:middle line:84%
So I think we cannot do anything
better and then follow the flow

00:47:56.580 --> 00:48:02.460 align:middle line:84%
of development and trying
to be, in our terminology,

00:48:02.460 --> 00:48:09.150 align:middle line:84%
as open and receptive for this
vision of Auroville that is

00:48:09.150 --> 00:48:10.140 align:middle line:90%
already there.

00:48:10.140 --> 00:48:19.210 align:middle line:90%


00:48:19.210 --> 00:48:22.720 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:48:22.720 --> 00:48:26.740 align:middle line:84%
>> Here there is a mix
of culture and race.

00:48:26.740 --> 00:48:28.390 align:middle line:90%
It is not easy.

00:48:28.390 --> 00:48:31.770 align:middle line:84%
Many can't take it,
despite their goodwill.

00:48:31.770 --> 00:48:34.980 align:middle line:10%
They can't handle the heat,
the tensions, or the work

00:48:34.980 --> 00:48:37.560 align:middle line:10%
that one is supposed to do here.

00:48:37.560 --> 00:48:40.200 align:middle line:84%
It is a kind of
natural selection.

00:48:40.200 --> 00:48:44.310 align:middle line:84%
At a certain point, those
who don't manage leave.

00:48:44.310 --> 00:48:45.930 align:middle line:90%
But it does not mean anything.

00:48:45.930 --> 00:48:49.020 align:middle line:84%
There are also other people who
have worked here for many years

00:48:49.020 --> 00:48:51.300 align:middle line:84%
and who take abroad what
they have learned here.

00:48:51.300 --> 00:48:53.760 align:middle line:84%
And this is the way
things spread contagiously

00:48:53.760 --> 00:48:54.720 align:middle line:90%
throughout the world.

00:48:54.720 --> 00:49:11.042 align:middle line:90%


00:49:11.042 --> 00:49:12.540 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:49:12.540 --> 00:49:22.390 align:middle line:90%


00:49:22.390 --> 00:49:26.980 align:middle line:10%
>> Becoming Aurovillian opened
my eyes to see much more.

00:49:26.980 --> 00:49:31.170 align:middle line:10%
And it is grace
that I started deep,

00:49:31.170 --> 00:49:33.550 align:middle line:10%
rediscovering my own culture.

00:49:33.550 --> 00:49:37.150 align:middle line:84%
I think I should
thank Mother for that.

00:49:37.150 --> 00:49:40.700 align:middle line:84%
>> There have been many attempts
at creating an ideal city

00:49:40.700 --> 00:49:42.580 align:middle line:90%
throughout history.

00:49:42.580 --> 00:49:45.730 align:middle line:84%
Aurovillians have chosen the
path traced by The Mother

00:49:45.730 --> 00:49:49.420 align:middle line:84%
and Sri Aurobindo, the search
for a new consciousness, which

00:49:49.420 --> 00:49:51.910 align:middle line:90%
is essential for human unity.

00:49:51.910 --> 00:49:55.780 align:middle line:84%
For 30 years, the experiment
in South India resists,

00:49:55.780 --> 00:49:58.690 align:middle line:84%
suffers setbacks,
and advances again,

00:49:58.690 --> 00:50:01.510 align:middle line:84%
thus giving the impression
that the best craftsmen,

00:50:01.510 --> 00:50:05.920 align:middle line:84%
but also the most dangerous
enemy of this ideal, is man.

00:50:05.920 --> 00:50:08.140 align:middle line:84%
This confronts us
with a question.

00:50:08.140 --> 00:50:11.730 align:middle line:90%
Can man live up to his ideals?

00:50:11.730 --> 00:50:13.300 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:50:13.300 --> 00:50:15.820 align:middle line:10%
>> The simple fact of
confronting humanity with its

00:50:15.820 --> 00:50:18.370 align:middle line:10%
ideals provides the answer.

00:50:18.370 --> 00:50:22.430 align:middle line:10%
Because these ideals were made
and conceived by human beings.

00:50:22.430 --> 00:50:24.910 align:middle line:84%
The simple fact of thinking
that such and such thing

00:50:24.910 --> 00:50:28.260 align:middle line:84%
would be desirable
to describe an ideal,

00:50:28.260 --> 00:50:31.382 align:middle line:84%
this simple fact shows that
one should be able to live it,

00:50:31.382 --> 00:50:32.215 align:middle line:90%
to make it concrete.

00:50:32.215 --> 00:50:35.890 align:middle line:90%


00:50:35.890 --> 00:50:38.200 align:middle line:84%
>> You can go to the Himalayas
and the high mountain,

00:50:38.200 --> 00:50:39.700 align:middle line:90%
sit there and meditate.

00:50:39.700 --> 00:50:43.030 align:middle line:84%
You can also have
fulfillment or realization,

00:50:43.030 --> 00:50:45.880 align:middle line:84%
as we call them, through
purely meditation and so on.

00:50:45.880 --> 00:50:50.020 align:middle line:84%
But Auroville stands for
fulfillment through work.

00:50:50.020 --> 00:50:52.420 align:middle line:84%
Work which is
meaningful, work which

00:50:52.420 --> 00:50:55.300 align:middle line:84%
can regenerate the
environment, which

00:50:55.300 --> 00:50:58.780 align:middle line:84%
can regenerate the
human spirit and create

00:50:58.780 --> 00:51:03.080 align:middle line:84%
more level of understanding
and compassion among people.

00:51:03.080 --> 00:51:07.020 align:middle line:84%
So I think its message is very
relevant in today's world,

00:51:07.020 --> 00:51:09.700 align:middle line:84%
as after the
September 11th events,

00:51:09.700 --> 00:51:11.655 align:middle line:90%
this is the message of hope.

00:51:11.655 --> 00:51:13.300 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH].

00:51:13.300 --> 00:51:17.090 align:middle line:84%
>> No animal, no object, can
think about a better world.

00:51:17.090 --> 00:51:18.250 align:middle line:90%
And the admirable.

00:51:18.250 --> 00:51:21.430 align:middle line:84%
Marvelous thing is exactly
this capacity of man

00:51:21.430 --> 00:51:24.510 align:middle line:84%
not to be satisfied,
to be unsubmissive

00:51:24.510 --> 00:51:26.110 align:middle line:90%
and to always dream of more.

00:51:26.110 --> 00:51:30.070 align:middle line:84%
And then, maybe one
day, even realizing it.

00:51:30.070 --> 00:51:33.940 align:middle line:84%
